getConfigChannelsFor

public java.util.List<ConfigChannel> getConfigChannelsFor(User user)
Returns the config channels associated to this activation key It requires User info for credential checking.. This method raises a Lookup Exception if the passed in user does NOT have access to the config channels.

Parameters:
user - the User object needed for access credentials
